Compilation: 
Ensure that we are starting from scratch type on the command line: 
make clean 
Set the switch block style by defining SWBMODE on line 56 in main.cpp, default is CROSSBAR
Then to compile simply enter on the command line:
make 
Please note that all settings have been set in the make file (including scl enable devtoolset-2)

Runing the router:
The above compilation will generate the executable router, to run it on one of the ciruits simply type:
./router <filename>
where <filename> needs to be replaced by the circuit of interest.
